### Art of Karen - API Test File
### Use with REST Client extension in VS Code or similar tools

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001
@token = your_token_here

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Register New User
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "newartist@test.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "username": "newartist",
  "full_name": "New Artist Name",
  "role": "artist"
}

### Login (Artist)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "karen@artofkaren.com",
  "password": "artist123"
}

### Login (Admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@artofkaren.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### Login (Student)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "student@artofkaren.com",
  "password": "student123"
}

### Get Profile (requires token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update Profile
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "full_name": "Updated Name",
  "bio": "I am a passionate artist and educator",
  "website": "https://artofkaren.com"
}

### Get All Artworks (public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/artworks

### Get Artworks (with pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/artworks?page=1&limit=10

### Get Featured Artworks
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/artworks?is_featured=true

### Get Artworks by User
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/artworks?user_id=2

### Get Artwork by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/artworks/1

### Create Artwork (requires multipart/form-data - use Postman or curl)
# curl -X POST http://localhost:3001/api/artworks \
#   -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN" \
#   -F "image=@path/to/image.jpg" \
#   -F "title=My Artwork" \
#   -F "description=Beautiful piece" \
#   -F "category=Painting" \
#   -F "tags=[\"portrait\",\"oil\"]" \
#   -F "is_published=true"

### Update Artwork
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/artworks/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Artwork Title",
  "description": "Updated description",
  "is_published": true,
  "is_featured": false
}

### Delete Artwork
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/artworks/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get All Blog Posts
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/blog

### Get Blog Posts (with pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/blog?page=1&limit=5

### Get Blog Post by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/blog/1

### Get Blog Post by Slug
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/blog/slug/my-first-post-1234567890

### Create Blog Post
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/blog
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "My First Blog Post",
  "content": "This is the content of my first blog post. It can be very long with markdown formatting.",
  "excerpt": "A short excerpt about this post",
  "is_published": true
}

### Update Blog Post
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/blog/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Blog Title",
  "content": "Updated content here",
  "is_published": true
}

### Delete Blog Post
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/blog/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get All Videos
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/videos

### Get Videos by Artwork
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/videos?artwork_id=1

### Get Video by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/videos/1

### Create Video
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/videos
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "How I Created This Painting",
  "description": "Step by step process video",
  "youtube_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dQw4w9WgXcQ",
  "artwork_id": 1,
  "is_published": true
}

### Update Video
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/videos/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Video Title",
  "description": "Updated description",
  "is_published": true
}

### Delete Video
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/videos/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
